{"tid":186351,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 西煎雞扒配脆邊煎雙強雙腸三養辣雞炒麵","createTime":"2017-04-04T06:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T23:59:54.000Z","uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9445a640228b1246b2e7428bb2d3a3064f43c9cd","tid":186351,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/01c30142d70c16b8b8eef02e4b5832e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F01c30142d70c16b8b8eef02e4b5832e0.jpg&h=46b3228a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料:<br />\n雞扒3塊<br />\n廚師腸2條<br />\n強2隻<br />\n<br />\n醃料:<br />\n蒜頭1個剁蓉<br />\n鹽半茶匙<br />\n百里香1湯匙多少少<br />\nBASIL2茶匙<br />\n甜椒粉1湯匙<br />\n黑胡椒碎2茶匙<br />\n黑醋2茶匙<br />\n油1湯匙多D<br />\n<br />\n影片如下:<br />\n<br />\nPART 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UpgWfMX3Nmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUpgWfMX3Nmo&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0d00b23c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UpgWfMX3Nmo</a><br />\n<br />\nPART 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1QIrrthWq2E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1QIrrthWq2E&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=77a07222\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1QIrrthWq2E</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞扒做法慨述:<br />\n<br />\n1. 雞扒用以上醃料最少醃一個鐘, 最好醃3個鐘.<br />\n<br />\n2. 撥走雞扒既醃料先煎.<br />\n<br />\n3. 易潔獲, 唔落油, 落雞扒, 雞皮向下, 開細火煎.<br />\n<br />\n4. 見雞扒出油, 就用紙巾吸走D油, 重覆至表皮煎好.<br />\n<br />\n5. 煎15分鐘至雞皮乾身同脆, 反一反, 到肉果邊煎3鈕分半鐘.<br />\n<br />\n6. 完成.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煎雙強雙腸三養辣雞炒麵做法請看影片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a387557bcf3a4d1a5bce4f019223d748fc61d9","tid":186351,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:05:28.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c1df07a2da3241700d24ac84b9870ef8efa127","tid":186351,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弘b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de211a5eee54da14f8472543789cd2393f44dbba","tid":186351,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:10:48.000Z","msg":"塊雞扒好似好劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1149d14c70829fe479f884b7959c1bf27d3cfb80","tid":186351,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae0577faf8dea01b1d090b4d1953ae8a2d06187","tid":186351,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"雞扒好似好燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a41807c6c97fbb310fab58cd51f0bc05d0a6e57","tid":186351,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞扒好似好燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99be4e43d06d8e2ab0aa0690570fd63ce9c7a663","tid":186351,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4e73d8fdd1c70ccc62f41946bbb492d55f783f","tid":186351,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor